sentences.en: Webb lives across the river from St. Louis in East Alton, Illinois, which has allowed her to set records in both Illinois and Missouri. She has set the Illinois record for deadlifting at 237 pounds, and the Missouri mark for 215 pounds, both in age and weight groups.
